<div id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Capture funds through your community</h2>
        <div id="iphone-image">
            <%= image_tag "nonprofits/nonprofits-iphone.png" %>
        </div>
        <div id="grtab">
            <image_tag "nonprofits/nonprofits-grtab.png" %>
        </div>

        <div id="nonprofits-steps">

            <div id="nonprofits-step1">
                <p><span class="bignumber">1</span>We create a free mobile site and app for your supporters with integrated FoodCircles dining. Every purchase made on the site/app is 100% sent to you via check.</p>
            </div>

            <div id="nonprofits-step2">
                <%= form_tag nonprofits_path, method: :post do %>
		    <%= text_field_tag :organization, nil, :placeholder => "Organization" %>
		    <%= text_field_tag :name, nil, :placeholder => "Name" %>
		    <%= text_field_tag :email, nil, :placeholder => "Email" %>
		    <%= text_field_tag :website, nil, :placeholder => "Website" %>
		    <%= submit_tag nil, :class => "button" %>
		<% end %>
                <p><span class="bignumber">2</span>You talk to restaurants you know about joining your FoodCirles app. The partnership goes beyond your typical 1-time event and requires little upkeep post-signup.</p>
                
            </div>

            <div id="nonprofits-step3">
                <p><span class="bignumber">3</span>People use your app whenever they eat out. Plus we launch FoodCircles in your area. Both bring funds and awareness 365 days/yr without taking up staff time or event bandwidth.</p>
            </div>
            

        </div>
        
        
        
    </div>
</div>



